<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied></hi> tiruvāykkeḻvi muṉṉāka <hi rend="grantha">tribhu</hi>vaṉaccak<hi rend="grantha">ra</hi>vatti
<lb n="2" break="no"/>kaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrīrājarājade</hi>varkku yāṇṭu 2 kūvamāṉa tiyākacamu
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ttiranallūr Iruṅkaṉūr kiḻavarkaḷom Uṭaiyār tiruviṟ
<lb n="4" break="no"/>kolamuṭaiya nāyaṉār tirunāḷeḻuntaruḷum Iṭattut tiruve
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ḻucci mukkālattilum <unclear>paṭaittār</unclear> nāṅkaḷe Eḻuntaruḷuvittu varu
<lb n="6" break="no"/>kaiyāle Ivvāṇṭu mutal Iṉṉāyanārkku tiruveḻuccipa
